8. Real-World Workflow
	1.	Developer pushes code â†’ GitHub triggers CI.
	2.	CI runs tests, builds Docker image.
	3.	Push image â†’ Docker Hub/Registry.
	4.	CD tool (ArgoCD) detects new version.
	5.	Deploys to staging â†’ test â†’ production.
	6.	Monitoring + alerting.

